nk" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/hao-wang-19">Hao Wang</a></div></div></span></div><div class="AuthorInfo-detail"><div class="AuthorInfo-badge"><div class="RichText ztext AuthorInfo-badgeText">CFA，知之为知之，不知为不知</div></div></div></div></div><div class="AnswerItem-extraInfo"><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">7 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content=""/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="7"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/279193775/answer/514076092"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2018-10-19T09:45:18.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-10-19T09:45:18.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="1"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">可能是物种灭绝的科普太多，我对于濒危动物一直有一种印象，就是他们的灭绝是不可逆的，人类现在做的保护工作只是在减缓他们灭绝的速度而已。所以我小时候一度以为大熊猫陪伴我们的日子是有限的，可能几十年之后有一天我们再也见不到大熊猫了，每想到此还颇为伤感。直到有一天我看到了下面这条新闻：2016年9月4日，世界自然保护联盟(IUCN)在美国夏威夷宣布将大熊猫的受威胁程度从濒危降为易危。<b>原来濒危动物是真的可以救回来的，…</b></span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0